## Enterprise MTA Platforms

These tools are designed for large organizations with complex tech stacks, significant budgets, and dedicated analytics teams.

<%= render "articles/embeds/competitor_section", competitor: "bizible", level: 3, custom_name: "Adobe Marketo Measure (Bizible)" %>

**Best for:** Enterprise B2B companies in the Adobe/Salesforce ecosystem

| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Pricing** | Enterprise (custom, typically $50K+/year) |
| **Setup Time** | 3-6 months |
| **CRM Integration** | Deep Salesforce & Dynamics native |
| **Attribution Models** | Multiple parallel models |

**Strengths:**
- Native Salesforce integration—no data sync issues
- Can run multiple attribution models simultaneously
- Strong ABM (account-based marketing) support
- Part of Adobe Marketing Cloud ecosystem

**Limitations:**
- Expensive and complex implementation
- Requires dedicated RevOps resources
- Fixed rule-based models (less flexible than ML-driven)
- Heavy Adobe/Salesforce lock-in

**Best fit:** Enterprise B2B companies already invested in Salesforce + Adobe Marketo who need account-level attribution and have RevOps teams to manage it.

