## Unified Measurement Platforms

These tools go beyond MTA to include MMM and model flexibility—the triangulation approach.

<%= render "articles/embeds/competitor_section", competitor: "mbuzz", level: 3 %>

**Best for:** Teams wanting flexible, server-side attribution without enterprise pricing

| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Pricing** | Free (<%= free_event_limit_display %> events), $29/mo (1M), $99/mo (5M), $299/mo (25M) |
| **Setup Time** | 10 minutes |
| **Tracking** | Server-side (95%+ event capture) |
| **Unique Feature** | 8 attribution models + custom rules |

**Strengths:**
- Server-side tracking bypasses ad blockers—captures 95%+ of events vs 70% with client-side
- 8 built-in models: First Touch, Last Touch, Linear, Time Decay, U-Shaped, W-Shaped, Markov Chain, Shapley Value
- Custom attribution models via simple rule editor—define your own logic in minutes
- Side-by-side model comparison shows how credit shifts between channels
- LTV attribution tracks recurring revenue back to original acquisition
- Native SDKs for Shopify, Rails, Django, Laravel, Node.js—no tag manager required
- Transparent pricing, no sales calls, export everything anytime

